OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised about people
OL,7,Fforcing family members to vote in a
OL,8,Fcertain way in the crunch Gorton and
OL,9,FDenton by-election.
OL,11,FAfter polls closed on Thursday night,
OL,12,Fan election observer group warned it
OL,13,Fhad witnessed family voting ` an
OL,14,Fillegal practice where two voters use
OL,15,Fone polling booth and potentially
OL,16,Fdirect each other on voting ` in 68%
OL,17,Fof polling stations observed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
