PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FDemocracy Volunteers' intervention has
OL,7,Fcaused consternation among the top
OL,8,Fthree parties and threatens to
OL,9,Fovershadow the counting of votes.
OL,11,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,12,Fsaid the report was "extremely
OL,13,Fworrying and concerning," Reform UK's
OL,14,FNigel Farage said it raised "questions
OL,15,Fabout the integrity of the democratic
OL,16,Fprocess in predominantly Muslim
OL,17,Fareas," and Green Party leader Zack
OL,18,FPolanski suggested he would back a
OL,19,Fprobe into the issue.
OL,26,@tD@UOUuD@YO]vD@]OUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FDemocracy Volunteers said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "Today we have seen
OL,8,Fconcerningly high levels of family
OL,9,Fvoting in Gorton and Denton.
OL,11,F"Based on our assessment of today's
OL,12,Fobservations, we have seen the highest
OL,13,Flevels of family voting at any
OL,14,Felection in our 10-year history of
OL,15,Fobserving elections in the UK.
OL,17,F"We rarely issue a report on the night
OL,18,Fof an election, but the data we have
OL,19,Fcollected today on family voting, when
OL,20,Fcompared to other recent by-elections,
OL,21,Fis extremely high.
OL,26,@oD@LOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,F"In the other recent Westminster
OL,7,Fparliamentary by-election in Runcorn
OL,8,Fand Helsby we saw family voting in 12%
OL,9,Fof polling stations, affecting 1% of
OL,10,Fvoters.
OL,12,F"In Gorton and Denton, we observed
OL,13,Ffamily voting in 68% of polling
OL,14,Fstations, affecting 12% of those
OL,15,Fvoters observed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
