PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FThe organisation said it attended 22
OL,7,Fof the 45 polling stations in the
OL,8,Fconstituency, spending 30 to 45
OL,9,Fminutes in each, and witnessed family
OL,10,Fvoting in 15 of the 22 polling
OL,11,Fstations observed.
OL,13,FThe group said they observed a sample
OL,14,Fof 545 individuals casting their vote
OL,15,Fand saw 32 cases of family voting in
OL,16,Ftotal, including nine cases in one
OL,17,Fpolling station.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
