FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FManchester City Council hit back that
OL,7,Fno issues had been reported and said
OL,8,Fit was "extremely disappointing" that
OL,9,FDemocracy Volunteers waited until
OL,10,Fafter the close of polls to make the
OL,11,Fclaims.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the acting
OL,14,Freturning officer at the by-election
OL,15,Fsaid: "Polling station staff are
OL,16,Ftrained to look out for any evidence
OL,17,Fof undue influence on voters.
OL,19,F"No such issues have been reported
OL,20,Ftoday.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@`O]wD@GOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,F"If Democracy Volunteers were so
OL,7,Fconcerned about alleged issues they
OL,8,Fcould and should have raised them with
OL,9,Fus during polling hours so that
OL,10,Fimmediate action could be taken."
OL,12,FJohn Ault, director of Democracy
OL,13,FVolunteers, said the group had raised
OL,14,Fthe matter at polling stations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
