SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FHe told the Press Association: "It is
OL,7,Fa normal international standard not to
OL,8,Fissue a comment until after a voting
OL,9,Fhas finished, another accepted aspect
OL,10,Fof election observation is that you
OL,11,Fare encouraged to ask questions of
OL,12,Fstaff...
OL,14,F"We posed questions about family
OL,15,Fvoting in several polling stations and
OL,16,Fhow staff dealt with it when it arose."
OL,18,FLabour chair Ms Turley told BBC
OL,19,FNewsnight of the family voting
OL,20,Fconcerns: "That's not what we want to
OL,21,Fsee in our democracy.
OL,26,@nD@`OUvD@AOUxD@gO]|D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,F"So obviously we need to see the
OL,7,Fevidence and the report, and then make
OL,8,Fdue decision about what authorities
OL,9,Fshould look into this."
OL,11,FMr Polanski told the programme: "If
OL,12,Fthe recommendation is that there
OL,13,Fshould be an inquiry or further steps
OL,14,Fthen yes I'd support that."
OL,16,FReform UK's candidate Matt Goodwin
OL,17,Fsaid he was "deeply concerned about
OL,18,Fthe extent to which the Gorton and
OL,19,FDenton parliamentary by-election is a
OL,20,Ffree, fair, and democratic election".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]sD@aOUvD@[O]yD@MOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
