OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FThe contest in the Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fconstituency is seen as a major test
OL,8,Ffor Sir Keir Starmer's premiership.
OL,10,FLabour won Gorton and Denton in 2024
OL,11,Fwith more than half the vote but
OL,12,Fpolling suggested the party's
OL,13,Fcandidate Angeliki Stogia faced a
OL,14,Ftight three-way battle with Reform
OL,15,FUK's Mr Goodwin and the Greens' Hannah
OL,16,FSpencer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FThe result, expected on Friday
OL,7,Fmorning, is likely to have
OL,8,Fimplications for May's local and
OL,9,Fdevolved elections and shape the
OL,10,Fpolitical landscape ahead of the next
OL,11,Fgeneral election.
OL,13,FVictory would buy the Prime Minister
OL,14,Fsome breathing space after a period in
OL,15,Fwhich his leadership has been
OL,16,Fquestioned and Labour's popularity has
OL,17,Fplummeted.
OL,19,FDefeat would be likely to reignite
OL,20,Fspeculation over efforts to replace
OL,21,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
