PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772179261
OL,3,CConcerns raised over 'family voting'
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,6,FMs Turley said she was "really
OL,7,Foptimistic" about Labour's chances,
OL,8,Fbut cautioned: "Of course incumbent
OL,9,Fgovernment always find it difficult to
OL,10,Ffight by-elections."
OL,12,FMore than a thousand Labour activists
OL,13,Fwere out across the constituency and
OL,14,Fspoke to more voters than on any
OL,15,Fprevious by-election polling day,
OL,16,Fparty sources told the Press
OL,17,FAssociation.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@KO]pD@POUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
